02:32.402 --> 02:35.405
Over 12% deviation

02:32.402 --> 02:35.405
from vertical.

02:35.447 --> 02:37.532
Fair enough.

02:40.035 --> 02:42.203
Dad, look how high my kite is.

02:42.245 --> 02:44.205
Oh, that's great, son.

02:44.247 --> 02:45.457
That's terrific.

02:45.499 --> 02:47.126
You want to try?

02:47.167 --> 02:49.210
Uh, no.

02:47.167 --> 02:49.210
Why not?

02:49.252 --> 02:50.587
I don't like kites.

02:50.629 --> 02:52.840
What do you mean

02:50.629 --> 02:52.840
you don't like kites?

02:52.881 --> 02:55.092
I don't like kites

02:52.881 --> 02:55.092
and they don't like me.

02:55.134 --> 02:56.135
We-we just don't get along.

02:56.175 --> 02:58.219
You'd like it

02:56.175 --> 02:58.219
if you tried it.

02:58.261 --> 02:59.638
Come on. Just try it.

02:59.680 --> 03:01.222
Hold the string.

03:01.264 --> 03:03.475
(Hal groaning)

03:15.988 --> 03:17.114
(yelps)

03:17.156 --> 03:18.157
Hey, Lois.

03:18.197 --> 03:20.951
Karen, what are you

03:18.197 --> 03:20.951
doing out there?

03:20.993 --> 03:22.828
Come on in.

03:22.870 --> 03:23.829
I'm sorry.

03:23.871 --> 03:25.539
I didn't mean to lurk.

03:25.580 --> 03:27.875
I was working up the nerve

03:25.580 --> 03:27.875
to talk to you.

03:27.916 --> 03:29.417
Are you okay?

03:29.459 --> 03:32.087
You look different.

03:32.129 --> 03:33.254
I'm sober.

03:33.296 --> 03:34.464
Oh.

03:34.506 --> 03:36.717
Yeah, after I drove across

03:34.506 --> 03:36.717
