03:39.302 --> 03:40.261
Good for you.

03:40.303 --> 03:42.139
Yeah, thanks.

03:40.303 --> 03:42.139
I'm doing really great.

03:42.181 --> 03:43.264
Anyway, I'm up to the part

03:43.306 --> 03:45.266
where I'm supposed

03:43.306 --> 03:45.266
to make amends

03:45.308 --> 03:46.852
to the people that I've hurt.

03:46.894 --> 03:48.645
What did you

03:46.894 --> 03:48.645
ever do to me?

03:48.687 --> 03:50.480
Remember New Year's

03:48.687 --> 03:50.480
at Deb and Rich's

03:50.522 --> 03:53.108
where everyone was kissing

03:50.522 --> 03:53.108
at midnight?

03:53.150 --> 03:54.109
Yeah.

03:54.151 --> 03:55.569
Well, when I kissed

03:54.151 --> 03:55.569
your husband,

03:55.610 --> 03:58.572
I kind of...

03:55.610 --> 03:58.572
stuck my tongue in his mouth.

03:58.613 --> 04:00.281
I mean,

03:58.613 --> 04:00.281
I felt really terrible.

04:00.323 --> 04:01.282
And then after that

04:01.324 --> 04:03.118
I put my cigarette out

04:01.324 --> 04:03.118
in Rich's toupee.

04:03.160 --> 04:05.286
And those things go up

04:03.160 --> 04:05.286
so quickly, I had...

04:05.328 --> 04:07.915
You were French-kissing

04:05.328 --> 04:07.915
my husband?

04:07.956 --> 04:09.083
Don't be mad at him, Lois.

04:09.124 --> 04:11.334
He pushed me away

04:09.124 --> 04:11.334
after like five or six seconds.

04:11.376 --> 04:13.461
Well, it was definitely

04:11.376 --> 04:13.461
no more than ten.

04:13.503 --> 04:14.588
And I'm sure

04:13.503 --> 04:14.588
the only reason

04:14.629 --> 04:15.881
he was moving his tongue around

04:15.923 --> 04:17.883
was because he was trying

04:15.923 --> 04:17.883
to say something.

04:17.925 --> 04:19.093
That's enough, Karen.

04:19.134 --> 04:20.219
I-I-I get it.

04:20.260 --> 04:21.887
I'm sorry.

04:21.929 --> 04:22.763
