04:34.357 --> 04:36.317
Is getting drunk all

04:34.357 --> 04:36.317
you ever think about?

04:36.359 --> 04:37.318
I mean, look at us.

04:37.360 --> 04:38.695
We work like dogs all day.

04:38.737 --> 04:40.989
We drink and then we work

04:38.737 --> 04:40.989
