04:41.031 --> 04:43.324
Is this really how

04:41.031 --> 04:43.324
you pictured your life?

04:43.366 --> 04:44.910
Ever since I was little.

04:44.952 --> 04:46.327
Why, what'd you picture?

04:46.369 --> 04:47.328
I don't know.

04:47.370 --> 04:49.164
There's just got

04:47.370 --> 04:49.164
to be more to life

04:49.206 --> 04:50.498
than getting

04:49.206 --> 04:50.498
falling-down drunk

04:50.540 --> 04:51.959
and behaving

04:50.540 --> 04:51.959
like a jackass.

04:52.000 --> 04:53.418
(laughing)

04:53.460 --> 04:55.545
Just looky what we found.

04:59.216 --> 05:01.135
You stole a totem pole?

04:59.216 --> 05:01.135
No, no, no,

05:01.176 --> 05:02.343
he asked to

05:01.176 --> 05:02.343
come with us.

05:02.385 --> 05:05.180
He hasn't shut up

05:02.385 --> 05:05.180
for an hour.

05:05.222 --> 05:06.431
You can't leave

05:05.222 --> 05:06.431
this here.

05:07.390 --> 05:08.391
People worship these things.

05:08.433 --> 05:09.935
It's like a sacred object.

05:09.977 --> 05:11.979
Do I have something in my teeth?

05:12.020 --> 05:13.396
Be honest.

05:12.020 --> 05:13.396
(laughing)

05:13.438 --> 05:14.940
What is wrong with you people?!

05:14.982 --> 05:17.358
You see a symbol

05:14.982 --> 05:17.358
of a world

05:17.400 --> 05:19.444
beyond scraping grease,

05:17.400 --> 05:19.444
and your first thought is,

05:19.486 --> 05:21.404
let's profane it

05:19.486 --> 05:21.404
in our cabin?

05:21.446 --> 05:24.616
Don't you have any respect

05:21.446 --> 05:24.616
for anything?!

05:25.408 --> 05:26.785
Look, a penny.

05:26.827 --> 05:27.953
It's mine!

05:27.995 --> 05:29.163
I saw it first!

05:29.204 --> 05:30.622
