05:53.895 --> 05:55.314
it doesn't give you

05:53.895 --> 05:55.314
the right

05:55.396 --> 05:56.315
to be nasty.

05:56.355 --> 05:57.398
If you keep this up,

05:57.440 --> 05:58.692
you're not going

05:57.440 --> 05:58.692
to have any friends.

05:58.733 --> 06:01.402
You think you know

05:58.733 --> 06:01.402
what everybody's problem is?

06:01.444 --> 06:02.403
Well, guess what,

06:01.444 --> 06:02.403
you don't.

06:02.445 --> 06:04.698
You think you're so smart

06:02.445 --> 06:04.698
and together

06:04.739 --> 06:07.909
and that no one notices

06:04.739 --> 06:07.909
what an unhappy little person

06:07.951 --> 06:09.244
you are.

06:09.286 --> 06:10.411
I'm sorry.

06:10.453 --> 06:11.412
I'm not going to stroke

06:11.454 --> 06:14.208
your fragile ego

06:11.454 --> 06:14.208
by confiding in you.

06:14.249 --> 06:15.250
Oh, yeah?

06:15.292 --> 06:17.252
Well, you're on fire.

06:17.294 --> 06:18.837
(screaming)

06:27.054 --> 06:28.930
(gasps)

06:28.972 --> 06:30.974
Mommy.

06:36.063 --> 06:37.647
CYNTHIA:

06:36.063 --> 06:37.647
How could you

06:36.063 --> 06:37.647
do that to me?

06:37.689 --> 06:39.691
You were on fire.

06:37.689 --> 06:39.691
I was just trying to help.

06:39.733 --> 06:41.526
How does yelling,

06:39.733 --> 06:41.526
"Oh, my God,

06:41.568 --> 06:43.653
where did those

06:41.568 --> 06:43.653
come from?" help?

06:43.695 --> 06:44.654
I'm sorry.

06:44.696 --> 06:46.073
It just...

06:46.114 --> 06:47.241
you scared me.

06:47.282 --> 06:48.075
They scared me.

06:48.116 --> 06:49.450
I mean, they don't scare me.

06:49.492 --> 06:50.660
They startled me. I...

06:50.702 --> 06:51.536
I hate this.

06:51.578 --> 06:53.454
Everyone looks at me

06:51.578 --> 06:53.454
like you did.

06:53.496 --> 06:55.290
Like I'm some kind of freak.

06:55.332 --> 06:57.125
I was surprised, that's all.

06:57.167 --> 06:58.459
It's just really different.

06:58.501 --> 07:00.503
I mean, I would react

06:58.501 --> 07:00.503
