07:05.926 --> 07:07.719
You can't tell anyone!

07:07.761 --> 07:08.970
What are you talking about?

07:09.012 --> 07:10.180
Promise me.

07:09.012 --> 07:10.180
But...

07:10.222 --> 07:11.348
Promise.

07:11.390 --> 07:12.349
All right. All right.

07:12.391 --> 07:13.474
I promise.

07:13.516 --> 07:15.394
Come on. You're fine.

07:15.435 --> 07:18.521
This is just a change

07:15.435 --> 07:18.521
on the outside.

07:18.563 --> 07:21.400
I mean, inside

07:18.563 --> 07:21.400
you're the same.

07:22.525 --> 07:24.111
If you give people a chance,

07:22.525 --> 07:24.111
they'll see that.

07:24.152 --> 07:26.280
Will you stop staring at them?

07:26.321 --> 07:28.531
Am... am I staring?

07:28.573 --> 07:29.908
Dad, I've been thinking

07:29.950 --> 07:32.493
about how to fix

07:29.950 --> 07:32.493
your kite problem.

07:32.535 --> 07:35.080
I don't have a kite problem.

07:35.122 --> 07:36.206
It's okay, Dad.

07:36.248 --> 07:37.498
Maybe we could start

07:37.540 --> 07:40.127
with you explaining

07:37.540 --> 07:40.127
why you hate kites.

07:41.920 --> 07:44.505
Let me try it. I want to try.

07:44.547 --> 07:46.507
