07:49.928 --> 07:51.846
(gasps)

07:55.392 --> 07:56.935
Help me! Help!

08:01.564 --> 08:04.985
I just do! There doesn't need

08:01.564 --> 08:04.985
to be a reason.

08:06.569 --> 08:07.528
(clicking tongue)

08:07.570 --> 08:09.530
Doesn't Dewey

08:07.570 --> 08:09.530
ever have any homework?

08:09.572 --> 08:10.615
He seems to have

08:10.657 --> 08:12.533
an awful lot of time

08:10.657 --> 08:12.533
on his hands.

08:12.575 --> 08:14.535
Something wrong?

08:12.575 --> 08:14.535
Yesterday I had

08:14.577 --> 08:17.164
the most interesting

08:14.577 --> 08:17.164
conversation with Karen.

08:17.205 --> 08:18.539
She's in this program

08:18.581 --> 08:20.541
where you have to apologize

08:18.581 --> 08:20.541
to your loved ones,

08:20.583 --> 08:22.543
and it got me thinking...

08:22.585 --> 08:26.214
do I have anything that

08:22.585 --> 08:26.214
I need to apologize for?

08:26.256 --> 08:27.424
Okay, by you, you mean me.

08:27.466 --> 08:29.384
And since you're phrasing it

08:27.466 --> 08:29.384
as a question,

08:29.426 --> 08:31.052
it means you already

08:29.426 --> 08:31.052
know the answer.

08:31.094 --> 08:33.472
Karen told me that

08:31.094 --> 08:33.472
you French-kissed her

08:33.513 --> 08:34.555
on New Year's Eve.

08:34.597 --> 08:36.391
What? I did not.

08:37.225 --> 08:38.559
I can't believe it.

08:38.601 --> 08:41.396
You-You're actually accusing me

08:38.601 --> 08:41.396
of this?

08:41.438 --> 08:42.939
Why would Karen lie?

08:42.981 --> 08:43.815
Why would  I  lie?

08:43.857 --> 08:45.484
Lois, for the past 20 years

08:45.525 --> 08:46.567
yours has been

08:45.525 --> 08:46.567
the only tongue

08:46.609 --> 08:47.819
that's been in my mouth.

08:47.861 --> 08:50.447
Now, you're just going

08:47.861 --> 08:50.447
to have to believe that.

08:50.489 --> 08:51.572
I don't lie.

08:51.614 --> 08:53.658
So, are we going

08:51.614 --> 08:53.658
to fly kites tomorrow?

08:53.700 --> 08:56.577
Sorry, son, I have

08:53.700 --> 08:56.577
to testify at a

08:53.700 --> 08:56.577
murder trial.

08:56.619 --> 08:57.787
But darn it, you're my son

08:57.829 --> 08:59.789
and I want to go to

08:57.829 --> 08:59.789
the park with you.

08:59.831 --> 09:01.291
Thanks, Dad.

09:01.333 --> 09:02.417
The kids don't count.

09:02.459 --> 09:03.877
Hal, it wouldn't be

09:02.459 --> 09:03.877
such a big deal

09:03.918 --> 09:05.212
if you would just admit it.

09:05.253 --> 09:06.754
Oh, come on, Lois.

09:06.796 --> 09:09.466
What possible reason would

09:06.796 --> 09:09.466
I have to kiss Karen?

09:09.508 --> 09:10.591
You're a man.

09:10.633 --> 09:11.676
What is that

09:10.633 --> 09:11.676
supposed to mean?

09:11.718 --> 09:13.845
You have been with the same

09:11.718 --> 09:13.845
woman all these years.

09:13.887 --> 09:17.098
It's only natural

09:13.887 --> 09:17.098
to be a little... curious.

09:17.140 --> 09:18.433
About what?

09:18.475 --> 09:19.434
You mean to tell me,

09:19.476 --> 09:20.852
after all these years

09:19.476 --> 09:20.852
of marriage,

09:20.894 --> 09:23.646
you've never even so much

09:20.894 --> 09:23.646
as thought about another woman?

09:23.688 --> 09:26.024
What are you talking about?

09:26.066 --> 09:27.608
If you are just going

09:26.066 --> 09:27.608
to be ridiculous,

09:27.650 --> 09:31.112
there is no point in carrying on

09:27.650 --> 09:31.112
this conversation.

09:31.154 --> 09:34.491
But you are on notice.

09:40.663 --> 09:42.832
Wait! I want to talk to you!

09:47.670 --> 09:49.464
You are unhappy.

09:49.506 --> 09:50.882
Yes, I am.

09:50.924 --> 09:51.674
Why?

09:51.716 --> 09:53.676
I think

09:51.716 --> 09:53.676
I may have ruined my life.

09:53.718 --> 09:56.054
I left my family and friends

09:53.718 --> 09:56.054
to come up here.

09:56.096 --> 09:58.139
I was supposed

09:56.096 --> 09:58.139
to be finding myself,

09:58.181 --> 10:00.808
but all I feel is empty.

10:00.850 --> 10:04.062
I have the answer

10:00.850 --> 10:04.062
to your suffering, Francis.

10:04.104 --> 10:05.480
The answer is...

